{"data":[{"date":"00:39 04/07","title":"H\u00e0ng hot tuy\u1ec3n Nga ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1eafn t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u cho Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/hang-hot-tuyen-nga-tiep-tuc-ban-tin-hieu-cho-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u1ee5 huynh nh\u00e0 Aleksandr Golovin \u0111ang thi nhau \u201cth\u1ea3 th\u00ednh\u201d c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia Premier League khi sau cha th\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb9 anh l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a con trai.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/gau-nga-vao-tu-ket-co-nhung-gia-tri-lon-hon-ca-chien-thang-421-190169.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 G\u1ea5u Nga \u0111ang th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 vi\u1ebft n\u00ean c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ed5 t\u00edch \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018</span> t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ngay tr\u00ean qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111o\u1ea1t t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft sau khi h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 sau nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang may r\u1ee7i.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">X\u1ee9 s\u1edf b\u1ea1ch d\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111ang th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng m\u1edbi, t\u1eeb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Igor Akinfeev \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Artem Dzyuba hay si\u00eau d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb Denis Cheryshev, v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qu\u00ean ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t Aleksandr Golovin.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mua Golovin tuy\u1ec3n Nga sau World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mua Golovin tuy\u1ec3n Nga sau World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/hang-hot-tuyen-nga-tiep-tuc-ban-tin-hieu-cho-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mua Golovin trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111i\u1ec3n trai tu\u1ed5i 22 l\u1ecdt m\u1eaft xanh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb g\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m nay khi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 Arsenal, c\u00f2n gi\u1edd ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m th\u00e0nh London Chelsea. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Golovin th\u00ec c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edbt nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u \u201cth\u1ea3 th\u00ednh\u201d c\u1ee7a\u2026 ph\u1ee5 huynh nh\u00e0 anh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCon trai t\u00f4i c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a n\u00f3. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Sasha \u0111ang b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfng Anh r\u1ed3i, n\u00f3 t\u1ecf r\u1ea5t h\u0103ng say r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 trau d\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea5y.\u201d \u2013 \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Golovin cha v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ee3 \u00f4ng Svetlana ti\u1ebfp l\u1eddi:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u00fang v\u1eady, CSKA Moscow \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c CLB kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 con trai t\u00f4i nh\u01b0ng c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 chi ti\u1ebft nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o th\u00ec ch\u01b0a ai bi\u1ebft. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Sacha l\u00fac n\u00e0y th\u00ec ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec quan tr\u1ecdng b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Nga c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ed3n cho World Cup. Chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00f3i ti\u1ebfp sau khi \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u01a1n minh ch\u1ee9ng cho d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n th\u1eed s\u1ee9c \u1edf Premier League c\u1ee7a Golovin. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng Arsenal hay Chelsea c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i nhanh ch\u00f3ng x\u00fac ti\u1ebfn n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i sao n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga v\u1ec1 tay Juventus.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/cska-tu-choi-ban-golovin-cho-juventus-176-188909.html\">CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng World Cup cho \u0111\u1ea1i gia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-tien-gan-toi-golovin-172-189928.html\">Chelsea ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi sao s\u00e1ng World Cup</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhm-arsenal-nhan-hlv-unai-emery-hay-ngay-lap-tuc-mua-golovin-172-188557.html\">NHM Arsenal nh\u1eafn HLV Unai Emery: H\u00e3y ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c mua Golovin</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"867","checkdouble":"190313"},{"date":"01:40 04/07","title":"Sao s\u00e1ng Uruguay x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/gettyimages-988121142.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cha c\u1ee7a Lucas Torreira ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed1i quan t\u00e2m nghi\u00eam t\u00fac c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh London d\u00e0nh cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/uruguay-21-bdn-ngay-ronaldo-phai-ghen-ti-voi-song-sat-suarez-cavani-421-190051.html\" target=\"_blank\">Uruguay \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</span> m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 ghi danh v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p. Trong khi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Edinson Cavani t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u00ec tr\u1ea7m l\u1eb7ng h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng, Lucas Torreira \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ec1m t\u1ecfa th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f2i n\u1ed5 Cristiano Ronaldo b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal mua Torreira v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng sau World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arsenal mua Torreira v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng sau World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/gettyimages-988121142.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal mua Torreira v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1eaft ch\u1ebft c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i d\u1ea1ng v\u1eeba d\u00f9 chi\u1ec1u cao ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ed5i 1m7. Kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean g\u00ec khi Torreira tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau theo \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Arsenal trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n cha c\u1ee7a Torreira \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 con trai khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 c\u00e0ng th\u00eam l\u00fd do kh\u1ea5p kh\u1edfi m\u1eebng th\u1ea7m. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cT\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho con trai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Arsenal \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quan t\u00e2m nghi\u00eam t\u00fac v\u1edbi n\u00f3. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u01b0a c\u00f3 g\u00ec l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c h\u1ebft, nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Anh. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd ngay sau k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u00e0y th\u00f4i, n\u00f3 s\u1ebd bay \u0111\u1ebfn London \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Theo d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, Arsenal s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd tr\u1ea3 cho CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Sampdoria c\u1ee7a Lucas Torreira kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ee9 t\u01b0 c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y, sau h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Stephan Lichtsteiner, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bernd Leno v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 Sokratis Papastathopoulos.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/uruguay-vui-dap-nga-man-trinh-dien-an-tuong-cua-nhung-hang-hot-421-189571.html\">Uruguay v\u00f9i d\u1eadp Nga: M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u201ch\u00e0ng hot\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/neville-khen-ngoi-tan-binh-arsenal-sau-tran-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha-469-190073.html\">Neville khen ng\u1ee3i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Arsenal sau tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chot-thoi-diem-arsenal-cong-bo-tan-binh-25-trieu-bang-172-190091.html\">Ch\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Arsenal c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"866","checkdouble":"190314"},{"date":"00:08 04/07","title":"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: MU chia tay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u00e8 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2015/8/13/mu-troi-chan-thanh-cong-them-mot-sao-tre.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Jordan Pickford kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111\u00e3 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t huy t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng.</h2><h2>Pickford ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh v\u00e0 Colombia l\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u00ec v\u1eady, h\u1ecd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Spartak v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t tr\u00f4i qua kh\u00e1 nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a v\u1edbi \u00edt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nguy hi\u1ec3m t\u1eeb c\u1ea3 hai ph\u00eda. Nh\u01b0ng b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra khi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u1ea3 11m v\u00e0 Kane th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf ph\u00fat 57.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Colombia vs Anh Pickford ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 penalty h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Colombia vs Anh Pickford ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 penalty h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/pickford-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-can-pha-qua-luan-luu-quyet-dinh-cua-bacca.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pickford l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn Colombia vs Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nTrong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u01b0u ti\u00ean ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, Pickford ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng duy nh\u1ea5t b\u1ecb th\u1eed th\u00e1ch l\u00e0 c\u00fa s\u00fat xa c\u1ee7a Muriel \u1edf ph\u00fat 90+2. V\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Everton \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t pha bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i nguy cho Tam S\u01b0.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nD\u1eabu v\u1eady, Colombia v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Yerry Mina \u1edf pha \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c sau \u0111\u00f3. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i k\u00e9o nhau v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng thua.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t 11m, Pickford \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Bacca \u1edf lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, qua \u0111\u00f3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 th\u1ebf c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. V\u00e0 Eric Dier \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 c\u00f4ng Pickford khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a Tam S\u01b0 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<h2>Pickford ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 penalty</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-colombia-461-190305.html\" target=\"_blank\">Colombia vs Anh</span>, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap anh c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00fa s\u00fat quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 nh\u01b0 Bacca.<br />\r\n<em><br />\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 nhanh nh\u1eb9n. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m vi\u1ec7c m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n nh\u1ecf b\u00e9 b\u1edfi v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i \u1edf \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac \u0111\u00fang ch\u1ed7 khi c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u00e0 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i lu\u00f4n suy ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed sao cho th\u00edch h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m tay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Bacca. K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1t penalty, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\u201d.</em><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Colombia vs Anh:</strong><br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-trong-ngay-dt-anh-pha-dop-de-vao-tu-ket-469-190319.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb trong ng\u00e0y \u0110T Anh ph\u00e1 d\u1edbp \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-colombia-461-190305.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Colombia 1-1 (pen 3-4) Anh (V\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)<br />\r\n</strong><br />\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"865","checkdouble":"190315"},{"date":"00:52 04/07","title":"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Man Utd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u00e2n binh ai-c\u0169ng-kh\u00f4ng-bi\u1ebft-l\u00e0-ai","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/Chinh-thuc-MU-mua-thu-mon-Lee-Grant-chuyen-nhuong-tu-do-hinh-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Manchester United ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lee Grant t\u1eeb Stoke City theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do h\u00e8 2018 v\u00e0 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hai n\u0103m v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 35 tu\u1ed5i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c MU mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lee Grant chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c MU mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lee Grant chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/Chinh-thuc-MU-mua-thu-mon-Lee-Grant-chuyen-nhuong-tu-do-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lee Grant t\u1eeb Stoke City theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong th\u1eddi gian World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, HLV Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 BL\u0110 Manchester United v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t, Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lee Grant t\u1eeb Stoke City theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. R\u1ea5t nhanh ch\u00f3ng, t\u00e2n binh g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n 35 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cKho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man Utd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea5p \u1ee7 t\u1eeb t\u1ea5m b\u00e9 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eafm b\u1eaft c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi ao \u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch khi \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a CLB gi\u00e0u truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eebng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. T\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin nh\u1eefng kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u00edch cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi. C\u1ea3m \u01a1n m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00ec t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 trong th\u1eddi gian qua v\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ebfn khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u n\u1eefa r\u1ed3i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">MU mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lee Grant, t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 ba sau qu\u1ea3 bom t\u1ea5n Fred v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Diogo Dalot, ngay sau khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-chia-tay-johnstone-172-190315.html\" target=\"_blank\">chia tay \u201cc\u00e2y nh\u00e0 l\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1eddn\u201d Sam Johnstones</span> c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19, l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng 35 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd s\u1eafm vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n th\u1ee9 ba d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho David De Gea v\u00e0 Sergio Romero trong khung g\u1ed7 Old Trafford.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoi-nha-xac-nhan-mu-chuan-bi-co-tan-binh-thu-3-172-190176.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/8/nguoi-nha-xac-nhan-mu-chuan-bi-co-tan-binh-thu-3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoi-nha-xac-nhan-mu-chuan-bi-co-tan-binh-thu-3-172-190176.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn M.U chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3</span><br>\r\nTheo x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb nhi\u1ebfp \u1ea3nh gia Craig Norwood, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lee Grant chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"864","checkdouble":"190317"},{"date":"04:17 04/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb trong ng\u00e0y \u0110T Anh ph\u00e1 d\u1edbp \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-trong-ngay-dt-anh-pha-dop-de-vao-tu-ket.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup n\u0103m nay t\u1eeb tay Colombia. Sau \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">1 &ndash; \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n1 - \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2006.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Colombia vs Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Colombia vs Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/041352-3.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Colombia sau lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n1998 &ndash; Jordan Pickford l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty trong lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang \u1edf m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb pha c\u1ee9u thua c\u1ee7a David Seaman tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina \u1edf World Cup 1998.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n99 &ndash; C\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Yerry Mina l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 99 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi sau ph\u00fat 90 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n3 &ndash; Yerry Mina \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf World Cup 2018. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Miroslav Klose ghi 5 b\u00e0n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf World Cup 2002.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Colombia vs Anh\" title=\"Colombia vs Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/032245-3.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mina c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n92:33 &ndash; \u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi trong th\u1eddi gian b\u00f9 gi\u1edd hi\u1ec7p hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup<br>\r\n<br>\r\n6 &ndash; Harry Kane l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n trong 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh t\u1eeb th\u1eddi Tommy Lawton n\u0103m 1939.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n9 - Kane b\u1ecb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Colombia ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i 9 l\u1ea7n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Anh b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Alan Shearer (11 l\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia n\u0103m 1998).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n14 - Kane \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 14 b\u00e0n trong 10 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Southgate. Anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n trong c\u1ea3 8 tr\u1eadn \u0111eo b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Colombia vs Anh:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-colombia-461-190305.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Colombia 1-1 (pen 3-4) Anh (V\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-anh-vs-colombia-463-190303.html\">Colombia 1-1 (pen 3-4) Anh (KT): Tam S\u01b0 l\u00ea b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft sau lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"863","checkdouble":"190319"},{"date":"04:45 04/07","title":"Pickford ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 qu\u1ea3 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Bacca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/pickford-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-can-pha-qua-luan-luu-quyet-dinh-cua-bacca.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Jordan Pickford kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111\u00e3 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t huy t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng.</h2><h2>Pickford ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh v\u00e0 Colombia l\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u00ec v\u1eady, h\u1ecd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Spartak v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t tr\u00f4i qua kh\u00e1 nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a v\u1edbi \u00edt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nguy hi\u1ec3m t\u1eeb c\u1ea3 hai ph\u00eda. Nh\u01b0ng b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra khi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u1ea3 11m v\u00e0 Kane th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf ph\u00fat 57.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Colombia vs Anh Pickford ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 penalty h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Colombia vs Anh Pickford ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 penalty h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/pickford-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-can-pha-qua-luan-luu-quyet-dinh-cua-bacca.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pickford l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn Colombia vs Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nTrong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u01b0u ti\u00ean ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, Pickford ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng duy nh\u1ea5t b\u1ecb th\u1eed th\u00e1ch l\u00e0 c\u00fa s\u00fat xa c\u1ee7a Muriel \u1edf ph\u00fat 90+2. V\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Everton \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t pha bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i nguy cho Tam S\u01b0.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nD\u1eabu v\u1eady, Colombia v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Yerry Mina \u1edf pha \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c sau \u0111\u00f3. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i k\u00e9o nhau v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng thua.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t 11m, Pickford \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Bacca \u1edf lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, qua \u0111\u00f3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 th\u1ebf c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. V\u00e0 Eric Dier \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 c\u00f4ng Pickford khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a Tam S\u01b0 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<h2>Pickford ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 penalty</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-colombia-461-190305.html\" target=\"_blank\">Colombia vs Anh</span>, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap anh c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00fa s\u00fat quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 nh\u01b0 Bacca.<br />\r\n<em><br />\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 nhanh nh\u1eb9n. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m vi\u1ec7c m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n nh\u1ecf b\u00e9 b\u1edfi v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i \u1edf \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac \u0111\u00fang ch\u1ed7 khi c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u00e0 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i lu\u00f4n suy ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed sao cho th\u00edch h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m tay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Bacca. K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1t penalty, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\u201d.</em><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Colombia vs Anh:</strong><br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-trong-ngay-dt-anh-pha-dop-de-vao-tu-ket-469-190319.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb trong ng\u00e0y \u0110T Anh ph\u00e1 d\u1edbp \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-colombia-461-190305.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Colombia 1-1 (pen 3-4) Anh (V\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)<br />\r\n</strong><br />\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"862","checkdouble":"190320"},{"date":"06:16 04/07","title":"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau \u0111\u00eam l\u1ecbch s\u1eed sang trang cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/thay-gi-sau-dem-lich-su-sang-trang-cho-nguoi-anh-tren-cham-11m.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n n\u00e0o n\u1eefa! M\u1ed9t Tam S\u01b0 tr\u1ebb trung \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 trong lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 cha anh, tr\u00e1i l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh nh\u1ea5t, ng\u1ecdt ng\u00e0o nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u00ean ngang b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018!</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1i d\u1edf c\u1ee7a Sterling v\u00e0 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Raheem Sterling ch\u01a1i 33/38 tr\u1eadn Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p to l\u1edbn tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Manchester City. Anh ghi 23 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec1n 13 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a d\u1ea5u gi\u1ea7y in \u0111\u1eadm v\u00e0o th\u00e0nh t\u00edch chung ch\u1ec9 thua k\u00e9m \u0111\u00fang Mohamed Salah v\u00e0 Harry Kane.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Colombia vs Anh Ph\u00e1 l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n 11m v\u00e0 sang trang l\u1ecbch s\u1eed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Colombia vs Anh Ph\u00e1 l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n 11m v\u00e0 sang trang l\u1ecbch s\u1eed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/Du-am-Colombia-vs-Anh-Pha-loi-nguyen-11m-va-sang-trang-lich-su-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Colombia vs Anh: Sterling kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt hi\u1ec7n th\u1eddi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1eb5ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u d\u1eabn ch\u1ee9ng l\u1eafm, nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3i ng\u1eafn g\u1ecdn t\u00f3m l\u1ea1i: Raheem Sterling l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean thay v\u00ec c\u1eb1n nh\u1eb1n v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c tranh lu\u1eadn v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a xung quanh \u0111\u1ec1 t\u00e0i \u201cLi\u1ec7u r\u1eb1ng Sterling c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh hay kh\u00f4ng?\u201d, h\u00e3y h\u1ecfi Gareth Southgate, y\u00eau c\u1ea7u hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 g\u00ec c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb: C\u00e1ch tinh ch\u1ec9nh c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 khai ph\u00e1 t\u1ed1i \u0111a s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m ti\u1ec1m t\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Tam S\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa cho Tam S\u01b0, th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n Sterling g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, nh\u01b0ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n anh. Southagate thi\u1ebfu trong tay m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, v\u1eady n\u00ean Sterling \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00e9o v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o th\u1ee9 hai l\u00f9i s\u00e2u h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c Harry Kane. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng s\u1ef1 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m l\u1ea1i tr\u00ean gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd khi Sterling kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed t\u01b0 duy \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 vai tr\u00f2 l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm \u0111\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n cho ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbt v\u00e1t trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac Southgate n\u00ean tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i cho c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p Pep Guardiola h\u00e0nh lang bi\u00ean ph\u1ea3i s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap anh th\u0103ng hoa r\u1ed3i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-anh-vs-colombia-463-190303.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-colombia.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-anh-vs-colombia-463-190303.html\">Colombia 1-1 (pen 3-4) Anh (KT): Tam S\u01b0 l\u00ea b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft sau lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng</span><br>\r\nT\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 bi k\u1ecbch \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Tam S\u01b0 khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd v\u00e0 \u1edf lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Henderson l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean s\u00fat h\u1ecfng (c\u1ea7n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juan Cuadrado kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i James Rodriguez<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">James Rodriguez \u0111\u00edch th\u1ecb l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Colombia v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1edfi v\u1ebb \u0111i\u1ec3n trai th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea3 trong l\u00fac kh\u00f3c c\u1ee7a anh. Ng\u00f4i sao Real Madrid/Bayern Munich l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng anh v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng cho m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn knock-out World Cup ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda. Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n bu\u1ed9c l\u00f2ng g\u1ea1ch t\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t, Jose Pekerman th\u1eadm ch\u00ed kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1n s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau \u0111\u00eam l\u1ecbch s\u1eed sang trang cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau \u0111\u00eam l\u1ecbch s\u1eed sang trang cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/Thay-gi-sau-dem-lich-su-sang-trang-cho-nguoi-Anh-tren-cham-11m-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m Colombia vs Anh: Juan Cuadrado \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i James Rodriguez</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Colombia m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c Juan Cuadrado ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Santiago Arias \u0111\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 h\u01a1n, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Juventus kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00f9i s\u00e2u ki\u1ebfm b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 tr\u00e1i l\u1ea1i, anh d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 \u201cc\u1eafm r\u1ec5\u201d ph\u00eda tr\u00ean v\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, Cuadrado \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p s\u1ef1 \u01b0u \u00e1i \u0111\u00f3, v\u1edbi 85% t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, r\u00ea d\u1eaft c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3\u2026 c\u00e2u l\u1ed7i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o. Tuy nhi\u00ean r\u1ed3i, anh \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t thi\u00ean t\u00e0i nh\u01b0 James \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t b\u1eb1ng s\u1ee9c s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng 27 tu\u1ed5i, Colombia thi\u1ebfu \u0111i h\u1eb3n s\u1ef1 tinh t\u1ebf, m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 trong t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t n\u1ed5i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec James c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c may m\u1eafn tho\u00e1ng m\u1ec9m c\u01b0\u1eddi<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea3n l\u0129nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Harry Kane<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 ph\u00fat 36 gi\u00e2y, Harry Kane \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee3i l\u00e2u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1ecb Carlos Sanchez nh\u1ea3y b\u1ed5 l\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba Colombia cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00ean ch\u1ea5m penalty \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t David Ospina. C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi 4 ph\u00fat 42 gi\u00e2y cho qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Kane Colombia vs Anh\" title=\"Harry Kane Colombia vs Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/harry-kane-noi-gi-sau-khi-cung-nuoc-nha-thay-doi-lich-su.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m Colombia vs Anh: Harry Kane x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh Tam S\u01b0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 8-9 d\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1eb5ng trong th\u00e2m t\u00e2m ng\u00f4i sao Tottenham khi ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ef1ng v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ph\u1edbt l\u1edd s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i d\u1eef d\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, r\u1ed3i r\u1ec9a tay h\u1eb1m h\u00e8 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 chi\u00eau tr\u00f2 g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p t\u00e2m l\u00fd tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. Sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, Harry Kane th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea3 ba v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cho c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1n n\u00e0o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu ng\u00fat ng\u00e0n \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Harry Kane g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 v\u1eady th\u00ec \u0111\u00fang, anh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t t\u1eeb chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh (ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t Jordan Henderson su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa \u0111\u01b0a Tam S\u01b0 v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm sau qu\u1ea3 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u h\u1ecfng \u0103n duy nh\u1ea5t). D\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng xa h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ea3 danh s\u00e1ch Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 d\u00e0nh c\u1ea3 v\u00e0 ch\u1edd s\u1eb5n Harry Kane r\u1ed3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed cho c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00fang r\u1ed3i, Harry Kane c\u0169ng d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang r\u1ee7i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n may cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh n\u1eefa, v\u1edbi c\u00fa g\u0103m b\u00f3ng s\u1ec7t v\u00e0o g\u00f3c ch\u1ebft khung th\u00e0nh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u00e1ng kinh ng\u1ea1c trong th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1ee1 v\u1ee5n tinh th\u1ea7n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 l\u00fac n\u00e0o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jordan Pickford Colombia vs Anh\" title=\"Jordan Pickford Colombia vs Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m Colombia vs Anh: C\u00fa bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c c\u1ee7a Jordan Pickford</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i, ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed. Tam S\u01b0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng ph\u00e1 d\u1edbp l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Euro su\u1ed1t g\u1ea7n 30 n\u0103m qua, v\u00e0 n\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh h\u01a1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi ch\u00ednh h\u1ecd m\u1edbi l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u00fat h\u1ecfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc r\u1ed3i l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c nh\u1edd <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/pickford-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-can-pha-qua-luan-luu-quyet-dinh-cua-bacca-469-190320.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0111\u00f4i b\u00e0n tay c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Jordan Pickford</span> v\u00e0 x\u00e0 ngang khung th\u00e0nh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n nh\u01b0ng ng\u1ecdt ng\u00e0o v\u00e0 tr\u00ean h\u1ebft x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t Colombia h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 uy hi\u1ebfp khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh h\u1ed9 ph\u00e1p c\u1ee7a Yerry Mina. Anh s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 ph\u00fat 90+3, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trong 30 ph\u00fat ti\u1ebfp theo c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n n\u00e3o t\u1eeb kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 11m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng Anh ch\u1ecbu \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u00e2m l\u00fd n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 ra sao khi b\u1ecb g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t hai ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ef1ng nh\u1eefng chi\u00eau tr\u00f2 ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o \u0111\u00fang ch\u1ea5t Nam M\u1ef9, r\u1ed3i n\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n truy\u1ec1n t\u1eeb c\u00e1c th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 cha anh, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i trung b\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Colombia vs Anh\" title=\"Colombia vs Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/thay-gi-sau-dem-lich-su-sang-trang-cho-nguoi-anh-tren-cham-11m.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m Colombia vs Anh: Tam S\u01b0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1ecdt ng\u00e0o h\u01a1n khi ph\u00e1 l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n 11m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng Colombia, th\u1eafng qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, th\u1eafng n\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh, th\u1eafng ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n n\u00e0o ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t c\u00fa l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng ngay tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u. T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai thu\u1ed9c c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 d\u00e0n Tam S\u01b0 tr\u1ebb trung n\u00e0y, v\u1edbi con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 28 n\u0103m, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed kh\u00f4ng ai c\u1ea5m m\u1ed9ng m\u01a1 xa h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u1edbi chung k\u1ebft hay c\u00fap v\u00e0ng, khi tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft h\u1ecd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1eeda \u1ea3i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n r\u1ed3i Nga ho\u1eb7c Croatia ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng v\u1eadt c\u1ea3n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t mang t\u00ean Colombia v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-noi-gi-sau-khi-cung-nuoc-nha-thay-doi-lich-su-421-190322.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/harry-kane-noi-gi-sau-khi-cung-nuoc-nha-thay-doi-lich-su.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-noi-gi-sau-khi-cung-nuoc-nha-thay-doi-lich-su-421-190322.html\">Harry Kane n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi c\u00f9ng n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"861","checkdouble":"190321"},{"date":"06:34 04/07","title":"Trippier l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Colombia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/trippier-len-tieng-nhan-loi-ve-ban-go-hoa-cua-colombia.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Kieran Trippier kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Colombia \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u00f3 l\u1ed7i l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a anh.</h2><h2>Colombia g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Colombia \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> v\u1edbi t\u00e2m th\u1ebf c\u1eeda tr\u00ean. Tuy v\u1eady, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Southgate v\u1eabn ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m d\u1ed3n qu\u00e2n l\u00ean \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTam S\u01b0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i hi\u1ebfm hoi \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, m\u1ed9t sai l\u1ea7m ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n c\u1ee7a Carlos Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 mang l\u1ea1i qu\u1ea3 penalty cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh. V\u00e0 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t, Kane \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n gi\u00fap \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Southgate v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh b\u00e0y binh b\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 kh\u00e1 b\u00e0i b\u1ea3n v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 s\u01a1 h\u1edf n\u00e0o. \u0110\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb Yerry Mina ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u d\u0169ng m\u00e3nh t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c ch\u1ebfch b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<h2>Trippier nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n thua\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trippier l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Trippier l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/trippier-len-tieng-nhan-loi-ve-ban-go-hoa-cua-colombia.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Trippier nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea5t r\u1ed3i n\u1ea3y v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh. Trippier l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f3. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Spurs \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n sai \u0111\u1ed9 n\u1ea3y c\u1ee7a qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n b\u00e0n thua cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh tr\u00ean v\u1ea1ch v\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Trippier \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u00fa nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd anh ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd th\u00ec c\u00f3 l\u1ed7i l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. Khi \u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i \u0111o\u00e1n r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ee7 th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea5t n\u1ea3y l\u00ean. T\u00f4i th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n sai t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Sau b\u00e0n thua, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. \u1ede lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t g\u00f3c kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. V\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng th\u00ec c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o g\u00f3c \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u v\u1eeba qua\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Colombia vs Anh:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thay-gi-sau-dem-lich-su-sang-trang-cho-nguoi-anh-tren-cham-11m-421-190321.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau \u0111\u00eam l\u1ecbch s\u1eed sang trang cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-trong-ngay-dt-anh-pha-dop-de-vao-tu-ket-469-190319.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb trong ng\u00e0y \u0110T Anh ph\u00e1 d\u1edbp \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"860","checkdouble":"190323"},{"date":"06:51 04/07","title":"L\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, HLV Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/lot-vao-tu-ket-hlv-thuy-dien-khang-dinh-chua-muon-dung-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, nh\u01b0ng thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n m\u01a1 xa h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Andersson chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Th\u1ee5y S\u0129.\r\n</h2><h2>Viking g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng &ndash; ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn, v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 d\u00f9 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng \u00edt h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, khi Emil Forsberg d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang Akanji \u0111\u1ed5i h\u01b0\u1edbng, l\u00e0m b\u00f3 tay th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Sommer.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, HLV Andersson vui m\u1eebng h\u01a1n ai h\u1ebft v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i, v\u00e0 c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo kh\u00f4ng may ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn&rdquo; &ndash; HLV 55 tu\u1ed5i cho bi\u1ebft. &ldquo;To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c cho nhau c\u1ea3 trong l\u1eabn ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t huy s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Andersson chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 v\u00f2ng 1/8\" title=\"Janne Andersson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/lot-vao-tu-ket-hlv-thuy-dien-khang-dinh-chua-muon-dung-lai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Andersson chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 v\u00f2ng 1/8</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;B\u00e2y gi\u1edd, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t cho tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1eadm ch\u00ed kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 ai, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 v\u00e0o \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 60 n\u0103m, ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c t\u1eeb k\u1ef3 World Cup 1958 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh. N\u0103m \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft ch\u1eebng c\u0169ng t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1, b\u1edfi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn ngh\u0129 g\u00ec, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n cho m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1eb7t ra. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u00f3a m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean SV\u0110 St Petersburg v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f4 vang t\u00ean m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ti\u1ebfp theo. Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft \u0111\u00e2u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u1ea1 th\u1ea5p m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd bi\u1ebft gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Andersson chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Th\u1ee5y S\u0129.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-thuy-dien-vs-thuy-si-421-190312.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/swe.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-thuy-dien-vs-thuy-si-421-190312.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 1-0 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t minh ch\u1ee9ng c\u1ee9 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 thua!</span><br>\r\nSau 90 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7y c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng t\u1ea1i SV\u0110 Saint Petersburg, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Andersson c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e9 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-thuy-sy-vs-thuy-dien-461-190299.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/224228-3.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-thuy-sy-vs-thuy-dien-461-190299.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 1-0 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 (V\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc \u00c2u th\u1eafng Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 1-0 t\u1ed1i 3/7, trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 h\u1ecd ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng \u00edt h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"859","checkdouble":"190327"},{"date":"06:49 04/07","title":"Henderson: \"\u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp \u0111\u00e1 penalty r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/4/henderson-dt-anh-da-tap-da-penalty-rat-ky.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jordan Henderson, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng penalty c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Colombia.</h2><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u00e0 m\u00e0n lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u l\u1ecbch s\u1eed</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean ch\u00e2n Colombia. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u00f3a l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Harry Kane tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m penalty v\u00e0o ph\u00fat 57.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng tr\u1edb tr\u00eau thay, khi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Southgate v\u00e0i ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd th\u00ec Colombia \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a. Xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i, Yerry Mina b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tung l\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Pickford. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Henderson ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1 penalty c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Henderson ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1 penalty c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/henderson-dt-anh-da-tap-da-penalty-rat-ky.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Henderson ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1 penalty c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Mina c\u0169ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> v\u00e0 th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u khi Tam S\u01b0 l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng k\u00e8m th\u1eadt ch\u1eb7t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh b\u1ecb k\u00e9o v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m. V\u00e0 \u1edf lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Jordan Henderson \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng trong khi Colombia c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 Uribe v\u00e0 Bacca. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Southgate \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n \u1edf lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang t\u1ea1i World Cup v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea7y hi\u00ean ngang.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Henderson ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac, c\u1ef1u \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Jordan Henderson c\u1ee7a Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp \u0111\u00e1 penalty r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Colombia.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Colombia c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a t\u1eeb pha b\u00f3ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a World Cup. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea5n t\u0129nh l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng lo\u1ea1t penalty \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng thua. Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1 penalty \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian. V\u00e0 HLV Southgate s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn ra 5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u00fat r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t. Pickford c\u0169ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Dier \u0111em v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cH\u00f4m nay, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi h\u01a1n t\u1ea5t th\u1ea3y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Colombia vs Anh:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/trippier-len-tieng-nhan-loi-ve-ban-go-hoa-cua-colombia-469-190323.html\">Trippier l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Colombia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-trong-ngay-dt-anh-pha-dop-de-vao-tu-ket-469-190319.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb trong ng\u00e0y \u0110T Anh ph\u00e1 d\u1edbp \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-colombia-461-190305.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Colombia 1-1 (pen 3-4) Anh (V\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"858","checkdouble":"190329"},{"date":"16:10 03/07","title":"\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf Spurs s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Harry Kane t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/dong-doi-o-spurs-san-sang-quyet-chien-voi-harry-kane-tai-vong-18.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB, nh\u01b0ng trong tr\u1eadn Anh vs Colombia t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Davinson Sanchez quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m b\u1eaft ch\u1ebft Harry Kane.\r\n</h2><h2>Sanchez s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng k\u00e8m ch\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e0n anh<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi\u1ebfn Tottenham ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u00ecnh, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Davinson Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean gia nh\u1eadp Premier League. \u1ede k\u1ef3 World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t tham d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Colombia.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0110T Anh cho m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. B\u1edfi v\u1eady v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB c\u00f9ng Harry Kane, Davinson Sanchez s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn trong nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 b\u1eaft ch\u1ebft \u0111\u00e0n anh &ndash; ng\u00f2i n\u1ed5 s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sanchez va Kane trong mau ao Tottenham\" title=\"Sanchez v\u00e0 Kane trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Tottenham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/dong-doi-o-spurs-san-sang-quyet-chien-voi-harry-kane-tai-vong-18.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Davinson Sanchez quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m b\u1eaft ch\u1ebft Harry Kane d\u00f9 h\u1ecd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i CLB</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 22 cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Harry Kane l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u, khi \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eed th\u00e1ch.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ea1i Tottenham. M\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng trai tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, nh\u01b0ng ngay khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1eddi CLB \u0111\u1ec3 tham gia nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 t\u1ea1i \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nhau m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00ecnh b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t sang m\u1ed9t b\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Colombia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft&rdquo; &ndash; Davinson Sanchez quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m b\u1eaft ch\u1ebft Harry Kane.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111\u00e3 cho \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Harry Kane ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Tottenham s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rooney-tuyen-anh-co-the-mo-mong-o-world-cup-nay-421-190252.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/31/rooney-tuyen-anh-co-the-mo-mong-o-world-cup-nay.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rooney-tuyen-anh-co-the-mo-mong-o-world-cup-nay-421-190252.html\">Rooney: Tuy\u1ec3n Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng \u1edf World Cup n\u00e0y</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111inh v\u1edbi Colombia v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Wayne Rooney \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o \u0110T Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-colombia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-47-co-den-tay-lieu-co-phat-421-190241.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/Colombia-vs-Anh.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-colombia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-47-co-den-tay-lieu-co-phat-421-190241.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Colombia vs Anh (1h00 ng\u00e0y 4/7): C\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn tay, li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 ph\u1ea5t?</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Colombia vs Anh v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018: R\u01a1i v\u00e0o nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i d\u1ec5 th\u1edf, Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u nh\u1ea5t trong v\u00f2ng 28 n\u0103m qua, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/southgate-dt-anh-se-khong-bi-loai-soc-nhu-o-euro-2016-469-190250.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/southgate-dt-anh-se-khong-bi-loai-soc-nhu-o-euro-2016.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/southgate-dt-anh-se-khong-bi-loai-soc-nhu-o-euro-2016-469-190250.html\">Southgate: \u0110T Anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1ed1c nh\u01b0 \u1edf Euro 2016</span><br>\r\nHLV Southgate kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u01a1i v\u00e0o c\u00e1i b\u1eaby t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m khi \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Colombia \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"857","checkdouble":"190283"},{"date":"16:23 03/07","title":"Ajax ch\u1ec9 mua l\u1ea1i Daley Blind v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/15/ajax-chi-mua-lai-daley-blind-voi-mot-dieu-kien.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ajax mua Daley Blind c\u1ee7a MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 ch\u1ec9 x\u1ea3y ra n\u1ebfu h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 28 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 Lan kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng g\u00e1nh n\u1ed5i m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u1edf Old Trafford.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ajax \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n mua l\u1ea1i Daley Blind</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDaley Blind ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Ajax trong 6 n\u0103m, t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2008 \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2014. Sau \u0111\u00f3 anh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Old Trafford v\u00e0o H\u00e8 2014 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 kho\u1ea3ng 16 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ajax mua Daley Blind ch\u1ec9 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ajax mua Daley Blind ch\u1ec9 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/31/Ajax-mua-Daley-Blind-chi-xay-ra-voi-mot-dieu-kien-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ajax \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n mua l\u1ea1i Blind</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o M.U, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Blind r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 trung v\u1ec7, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, \u1edf Old Trafford anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00f2n vai.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Mourinho, Blind kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 4 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Blind, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n M.U b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Blind v\u1edbi M.U ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o cho th\u1ea5y hai b\u00ean s\u1ebd gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/day-ben-do-moi-cua-daley-blind-neu-roi-mu-172-190201.html\">Ajax l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Blind nh\u1ea5t</span>, h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i H\u00e0 Lan. Theo The Sun, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0y, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ajax ch\u1ec9 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Blind v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ajax mua Daley Blind c\u1ee7a MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 ch\u1ec9 x\u1ea3y ra n\u1ebfu h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 28 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 Lan kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng g\u00e1nh n\u1ed5i m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u1edf Old Trafford.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Daley Blind\" title=\"Daley Blind\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/15/ajax-chi-mua-lai-daley-blind-voi-mot-dieu-kien.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ajax, Daley Blind bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u01a1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Blind \u0111ang nh\u1eadn 120.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u1edf M.U, ph\u00eda Ajax ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 60.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ajax c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3m 50% l\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBlind s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. N\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef v\u1eefng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i anh ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf M.U. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n anh bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"856","checkdouble":"190284"},{"date":"17:06 03/07","title":"Sao tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p n\u1eb1ng n\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi Sevilla t\u1edbi Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/sao-tuyen-phap-nang-nac-doi-roi-sevilla-toi-arsenal.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Michael Carrick ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jesse Lingard, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a M.U \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jesse Lingard \u0111ang tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jesse Lingard l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh M.U. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ghi t\u1edbi 14 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 5 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Michael Carrick ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jesse Lingard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Michael Carrick ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jesse Lingard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/carrick-len-tieng-ca-ngoi-jesse-lingard.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lingard \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o MU v\u00e0 \u0110T Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Lingard \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao anh \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c HLV Gareth Southgate trao cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 6-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama, Lingard \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t hay v\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-colombia-vs-anh-1h00-ngay-47-co-den-tay-lieu-co-phat-421-190241.html\" target=\"_blank\">Anh vs Colombia</span> trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U. NHM Tam s\u01b0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng Lingard c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0a Anh v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Carrick khen ng\u1ee3i Lingard</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Michael Carrick ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jesse Lingard, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a M.U \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lingard\" title=\"Lingard\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/1529345402644_lc_galleryImage_Soccer_Football_World_Cup.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Carrick khen ng\u1ee3i Lingard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i g\u1eb7p c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 15 tu\u1ed5i, \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 Lingard g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cS\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Lingard c\u00f3 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u0103ng tr\u1ea7m, nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. S\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Lingard s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Lingard \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Anh \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"855","checkdouble":"190285"},{"date":"16:19 03/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u gi\u1edd \u0111\u1eb9p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/nhan-dinh-thuy-dien-vs-thuy-si-va-du-doan-soi-keo-thuy-si-vs-thuy-dien.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u kh\u00f3 xem. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng ph\u00e2n t\u00edch d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1eeb h\u00f2a t\u1edbi th\u1eafng</strong><br>\r\n- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 2)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n th\u1eafng 2-1<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129<br>\r\nTh\u1eddi gian: 21h ng\u00e0y 3/7<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: S\u00e2n Saint-Petersburg<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n -0.90*0:0*0.85 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129<br>\r\nTBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: Nhi\u1ec1u -0.89*2*0.82 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, soi k\u00e8o, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch TL h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, soi k\u00e8o, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch TL h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/nhan-dinh-thuy-dien-vs-thuy-si-va-du-doan-soi-keo-thuy-si-vs-thuy-dien.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 21h ng\u00e0y 3/7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1eeb h\u00f2a t\u1edbi th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 n\u1ebfu n\u00f3i chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup t\u00ednh t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y th\u00f4i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. Ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i th\u00f4i, vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua H\u00e0 Lan \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 2 trong b\u1ea3ng, ch\u1ec9 sau Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng khen.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc VCK t\u1ea1i Nga, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ki\u1ebfn k\u00eau g\u1ecdi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n g\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i Zlatan Ibrahimovic. R\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Janne Andersson l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf cho th\u1ea5y trong vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 55 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00fang. Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng Ibrahimovic kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, nh\u01b0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 m\u1ea1nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thuy Dien thang Mexico 3-0\" title=\"Thuy Dien thang Mexico 3-0\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-mexico-03-thuy-dien.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng su\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 Ibrahimovic, h\u1ecd ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o cao k\u1ec1u v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i theo c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a anh. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng Ibra, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 h\u01a1n khi ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u m\u0169i \u0111a d\u1ea1ng h\u01a1n. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Scandinavi t\u1edbi gi\u1edd l\u00e0 mi\u1ec5n ch\u00ea. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 1-0. T\u1edbi tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c, h\u1ecd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ecbu thua b\u1edfi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t tuy\u1ec7t h\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Toni Kroos. Nh\u01b0ng khi b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o th\u1ebf hi\u1ec3m ngh\u00e8o, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f9ng l\u00ean d\u1eef d\u1ed9i. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Mexico 3-0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng F, tr\u00e1nh lu\u00f4n g\u1eb7p Brazil.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Zlatan Ibrahimovic se khong gop mat cung DT Thuy Dien.\" title=\"Zlatan Ibrahimovic s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u00f9ng \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/28/thuy-dien-se-choi-tot-hon-khi-khong-con-ibrahimovic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Thi\u1ebfu Ibrahimovic kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc \u00c2u</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nG\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t \u00f4ng l\u1edbn n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem nh\u01b0 may m\u1eafn v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f2n m\u1eebng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa khi m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 thi\u1ebfu \u0111i m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t. Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Costa Rica 2-2 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 m\u1ea5t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 bao g\u1ed3m Stephan Lichtsteiner v\u00e0 Fabian Schar.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a h\u1ebft, tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd b\u00f3ng l\u0103n, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Steven Zuber c\u00f2n l\u00ean c\u01a1n s\u1ed1t v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c tham d\u1ef1. Thi\u1ebfu \u0111i 3 m\u1eaft x\u00edch tr\u00ean, s\u1ef1 l\u1ed9n x\u1ed9n c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 l\u00e0 d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1eddi c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ec3 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/granqvist-phat-bieu-ve-ibrahimovic-va-thuy-dien-421-190211.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/24/granqvist-phat-bieu-ve-ibrahimovic-va-thuy-dien.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/granqvist-phat-bieu-ve-ibrahimovic-va-thuy-dien-421-190211.html\">Kh\u00f4ng Ibrahimovic, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1 hay h\u01a1n!</span><br>\r\n<span>Granqvist ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ibrahimovic. T\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n tin r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u00f4i khi l\u1ea1i gi\u00fap h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u hay h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 thi\u1ebfu \u0111i 2 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 Lichtsteiner v\u00e0 Fabian Schar. V\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 s\u1ebd thi\u1ebfu \u0111i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng, th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh tinh th\u1ea7n. Ngo\u00e0i ra, nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Lichtsteiner khi m\u1ea5t \u0111i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i. Qua \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng Forsberg c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd c\u00e0ng r\u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n h\u01a1n b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n \u1edf trung t\u00e2m, m\u1ed9t Johan Djourou n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng l\u00f3ng ng\u00f3ng khi k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Manuel Akanji s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 b\u1ea5t an. H\u1ecd ch\u01b0a k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhau ph\u00fat n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 ra sao kh\u00f4ng ai bi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Mitrovic ghi ban truoc Thuy Si\" title=\"tien dao Mitrovic ghi ban truoc Thuy Si\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/HLV-Mladen-Krstajic-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Serbia-vs-Thuy-Sy-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111ang b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi, t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 4 b\u00e0n. \u0110\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn HLV Vladimir Petkovic kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng b\u1edfi \u00f4ng v\u1ed1n \u01b0u ti\u00ean y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 54 tu\u1ed5i h\u1eb3n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y lo l\u1eafng khi \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ea7y h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1i c\u00e1ch Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Mexico 3-0 c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn Petkovic tr\u0103n tr\u1edf. B\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o th\u1ebf bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc \u00c2u \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5. 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 ch\u00fat n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee5y S\u0129 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n thay v\u00ec thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n ti\u1ec1m \u1ea9n nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ed7i lo v\u00e0 HLV Petkovic kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u1ea5y s\u1edf \u0111o\u1ea3n ra \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea9y tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n c\u1ef1c h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edbi d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c 2 tr\u00e1i ch\u1eb5n cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee9c t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng. Nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t sinh \u1edf cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi khi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 suy gi\u1ea3m kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. <br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1eeb h\u00f2a t\u1edbi th\u1eafng</strong><br>\r\n- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 2)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n th\u1eafng 2-1<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 9 (O 9)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng l\u1eafm l\u00e0 4 (U 4)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 3 (U 3)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 1 (U 1)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLong Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"854","checkdouble":"190286"},{"date":"17:37 03/07","title":"\u0110\u1ee9c ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \"t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3\" Joachim Loew","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/Low1.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV 58 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng \u0110TQG n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda World Cup 2018 \u1edf Nga.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c, v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi khi tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf Nga v\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-phai-chang-tuyen-duc-dang-tro-thanh-nhung-nguoi-anh-moi-421-189831.html\" target=\"_blank\">s\u1edbm b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018 ngay v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng</span> l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 80 n\u0103m, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ed5 sau hai tr\u1eadn thua nh\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Joachim Loew ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c sau th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Joachim Loew ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c sau th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Low1.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Joachim Loew s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ee9ng m\u0169i ch\u1ecbu s\u00e0o m\u1ecdi b\u00faa r\u00ecu ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Joachim Loew, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1ea7n d\u00e0 \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i m\u00f2n b\u1ea3o th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u v\u00ec v\u1eady \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c chia tay sau 12 n\u0103m \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb, ho\u1eb7c m\u1ed9t tr\u00e1t sa th\u1ea3i v\u00e0 kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n k\u1ebfch x\u00f9 b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 4 n\u0103m c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng, ho\u1eb7c HLV 58 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c trong \u00eam \u0111\u1eb9p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng khi theo th\u00f4ng tin ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2022. B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng \u00fd ki\u1ebfn tr\u00e1i chi\u1ec1u, HLV Joachim Loew s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng \u0110TQG n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 qua \u00edt nh\u1ea5t hai gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn n\u1eefa, bao g\u1ed3m Euro 2020 v\u00e0 World Cup 2022 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Qatar.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u1eabu sao, Joachim Loew \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u00e0m l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Euro 2022 m\u1edf m\u00e0n b\u1eb1ng hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Peru trong th\u00e1ng Ch\u00edn n\u0103m nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/joachim-low-thua-nhan-duc-dang-bi-loai-465-189795.html\">HLV Joachim Loew: \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tan-man/joachim-low-ban-linh-xua-cu-cua-tuyen-duc-dau-roi-392-190026.html\">HLV Joachim Loew:  B\u1ea3n l\u0129nh x\u01b0a c\u0169 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e2u r\u1ed3i?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"853","checkdouble":"190287"}]}